<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="20Aug1917"><font color="red">20 August 1917</font>, <cite>Selected Letters</cite> (JJ to Ezra Pound): &hellip; and if there is a prospect that your suggestion of some months ago will become a fact; I mean about <cite>Ulysses</cite>. You suggested that it could appear serially in <cite>Egoist</cite> and <cite>Little Review</cite> and thus bring me double fees. I am prepared to consign it serially from 1 January next, instalments of about 6000 words </div>
